The '''Margaret W. Rossiter History of Women in Science Prize''' is awarded by the [[History of Science Society]] for an outstanding book or article on the history of women in science.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hssonline.org/about/honors/the-margaret-w-rossiter-history-of-women-in-science-prize/|title=The Margaret W. Rossiter History of Women in Science Prize - History of Science Society|website=hssonline.org|accessdate=23 March 2018}}</ref> It is named after Professor [[Margaret W. Rossiter]], a pioneer in the field of the role of women in science.
